# Built Node addon (napi convention: `.node` extension). Built per-platform by
# `cargo +stable-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc build -p zpz-napi --release --features addon` (see src/lib.rs);
# prebuild packaging (optionalDependencies matrix) is a later phase — see docs/modules/napi.md's
# "Packaging layout" section.
*.node

# DSL rule packs copied from <repo root>/rules/dsl/ by the `prepack` script
# (scripts/copy-rules.mjs) so they ship in the published npm package. Build artifact — not
# checked in.
rules/
